Nice. Edited to fix a few minor formatting issues in the statement.

However there are several issues with the input format:
 - It would be nicer to have H lines of W integers (more human-readable for debug purposes and more consistent with the output format);
 - The stub currently corresponds to the format I've just described and not to the current format (of course that does not matter in C++ as cin indistinctly eats all kinds of blank chars); Ideally you don't have to change it, just use the nicer format;
 - Moreover there is an extra space at the end of all inputs (that also matters in some languages).
